{"tid":2232872,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下濕疹查呢隻潤膚膏有冇用/推介？","createTime":"2020-10-06T16:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T14:57:34.000Z","uid":66923,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"46ddf275d38794dceb7a561264366115ac89f015","tid":2232872,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PbPVAhz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPbPVAhz.jpg&h=1b399f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身濕疹一路查開呢隻潤膚膏保濕<br />\n早晚同沖涼後都都會查一次<br />\n其實呢隻有冇話會令到患處容易惡化/有冇咩副作用?<br />\n因為我見到下面篇野話唔好查呢隻<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/TopicalSteroidAddictionHK/posts/235124673996637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FTopicalSteroidAddictionHK%2Fposts%2F235124673996637&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=28d1ac36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/TopicalSteroidAddictionHK/posts/235124673996637</a><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇人都係查緊呢隻潤膚膏可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有冇話濕疹用邊隻潤膚膏好用推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3cf823257e6fc327505f9216ffbb560f199563","tid":2232872,"uid":194079,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T16:27:24.000Z","msg":"呢個好好用的，無副作用，好溫和👍🏻"},{"pid":"3c0c0e8bc0bf66fcd4335a2ecd26b365cbe92356","tid":2232872,"uid":194079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"皮膚科專科醫生史泰祖指出，Aqueous Cream（俗稱 A Cream或冷霜）及Emulsifying Ointment（俗稱 E Cream或豬油膏）是「平、靚、正」之選，公營醫療機構及不少皮膚科醫生也採用。<br />\n<br />\n可以聽下皮膚科專家講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1539424/名牌面霜真面目%E3%80%80醫生推介-35%20A%20Cream走天涯\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1539424%2F%E5%90%8D%E7%89%8C%E9%9D%A2%E9%9C%9C%E7%9C%9F%E9%9D%A2%E7%9B%AE%25E3%2580%2580%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB